Hector Soberon Lorenzo has an impressive net worth of $3 million

Hector Soberon Lorenzo’s Background

Hector Soberon Lorenzo, born on August 11, 1964, is a renowned Mexican actor. He is known for his roles in various movies and TV shows including “María la del Barrio” and “Idolos de Juventud.” He is also recognized for his work in films such as “Kamasutra: a tale of love.”
